{% comment %}
  PostJoy Brand Story - Factory Strength Section
  Style: Real manufacturing strength + bold brand storytelling
{% endcomment %}

<section class="postjoy-factory-story">
  <div class="postjoy-factory-bg-glow"></div>

  <div class="postjoy-factory-container">

    <div class="postjoy-factory-header">
      <p class="postjoy-factory-eyebrow">OUR FACTORY STRENGTH</p>
      <h2>Where Joy Becomes Real.</h2>
      <p>
        A great ride does not begin on the road. It begins inside the factory — where ideas become frames, components become complete eBikes, and every PostJoy promise is built with real manufacturing strength.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="postjoy-factory-stats">
      <div class="postjoy-factory-stat">
        <span>4</span>
        <p>Factory Buildings</p>
      </div>
      <div class="postjoy-factory-stat">
        <span>Multi-Line</span>
        <p>eBike Production</p>
      </div>
      <div class="postjoy-factory-stat">
        <span>Hands-On</span>
        <p>Assembly & Inspection</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="postjoy-factory-intro">
      <p>
        PostJoy is supported by <strong>four dedicated factory buildings</strong>, each playing an important role in the journey from components to finished electric bikes.
      </p>
      <p>
        From frame preparation and component fitting to assembly, protection, inspection, packaging, and shipment readiness, our production process is organized to keep every key detail under control.
      </p>
      <p>
        Inside our facilities, rows of eBikes are carefully assembled and prepared for riders around the world. This is not just where our products are made — this is where the PostJoy riding experience begins.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="postjoy-factory-showcase">

      <div class="postjoy-factory-card large-card">
        <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/postjoyebike_factory_2.jpg?v=1778343960"
          alt="PostJoy electric bike factory production line"
          width="1080"
          height="1920"
          loading="lazy"
        >
        <div class="postjoy-card-overlay">
          <span>Scale</span>
          <h3>Organized Production Capacity</h3>
          <p>Rows of finished and semi-finished eBikes show the scale behind every PostJoy delivery.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="postjoy-factory-card">
        <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/postjoyebike_factory_1.jpg?v=1778343960"
          alt="PostJoy eBike assembly and shipment preparation"
          width="2048"
          height="1536"
          loading="lazy"
        >
        <div class="postjoy-card-overlay">
          <span>Assembly</span>
          <h3>Careful Build Process</h3>
          <p>Every eBike is assembled, protected, and prepared before it leaves the factory floor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="postjoy-factory-card">
        <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/postjoyebike_factory.jpg?v=1778343960"
          alt="PostJoy electric bike assembly process"
          width="1080"
          height="1920"
          loading="lazy"
        >
        <div class="postjoy-card-overlay">
          <span>Control</span>
          <h3>Structured Workflow</h3>
          <p>A consistent production flow helps support stable quality across different models.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="postjoy-factory-card wide-card">
        <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/postjoyebike_factory_5.jpg?v=1778343960"
          alt="PostJoy electric dirt bike production facility"
          width="1536"
          height="2048"
          loading="lazy"
        >
        <div class="postjoy-card-overlay">
          <span>Product Lines</span>
          <h3>Built for Different Rides</h3>
          <p>From electric dirt bikes to commuter eBikes, our facilities support multiple product categories.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="postjoy-factory-card">
        <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/postjoyebike_factory_3.jpg?v=1778343960"
          alt="PostJoy fat tire electric bike factory"
          width="2048"
          height="1536"
          loading="lazy"
        >
        <div class="postjoy-card-overlay">
          <span>Power</span>
          <h3>Ready for Real Roads</h3>
          <p>Strong fat tire models are prepared for riders who need stability, comfort, and adventure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="postjoy-factory-card">
        <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/postjoyebike_factory_4.jpg?v=1778343960"
          alt="PostJoy GT series electric bike production"
          width="2048"
          height="1536"
          loading="lazy"
        >
        <div class="postjoy-card-overlay">
          <span>Detail</span>
          <h3>Built with Dependability</h3>
          <p>Behind every finished ride is a hands-on process focused on detail, protection, and reliability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="postjoy-factory-quality">
      <div class="postjoy-factory-quality-inner">
        <p class="postjoy-factory-eyebrow">FROM FACTORY FLOOR TO OPEN ROAD</p>
        <h3>Quality You Can Feel on Every Ride</h3>

        <p>
          A powerful motor means little without careful assembly. A long-range battery means little without stable quality control. A stylish design means little unless it is built to handle real roads, real riders, and real adventures.
        </p>

        <p>
          That is why we continue to invest in factory capacity, production organization, and hands-on quality management. Our manufacturing strength allows PostJoy to support different product lines while maintaining dependable standards across every batch.
        </p>

        <div class="postjoy-factory-confidence">
          <div>
            <span>01</span>
            <p>Confidence that your eBike was built with care.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>02</span>
            <p>Confidence that every component has a purpose.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>03</span>
            <p>Confidence that every ride begins long before the first mile.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="postjoy-factory-bold-line">
          At PostJoy, we do not just design the feeling of freedom. We build it, inspect it, protect it, and deliver it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .postjoy-factory-story {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 90px 20px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.22), transparent 34%),
      radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.12), transparent 32%),
      #080808;
    color: #ffffff;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-story * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-bg-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 160px;
    left: 50%;
    width: 420px;
    height: 420px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.12);
    filter: blur(90px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1220px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-header {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto 42px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: #ff7a18;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 2.2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-header h2 {
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 58px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -1.2px;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-header p {
    max-width: 790px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #d8d8d8;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.78;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 0 auto 52px;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-stat {
    padding: 24px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
    border-radius: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .postjoy-factory-stat span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 34px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-stat p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #cfcfcf;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-intro {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-intro p {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    color: #d6d6d6;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.78;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-intro p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-intro strong {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-showcase {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-auto-rows: 330px;
    gap: 22px;
    margin: 0 0 70px;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 330px;
    background: #151515;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
    border-radius: 22px;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 55px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
  }

  .postjoy-factory-card.large-card {
    grid-row: span 2;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-card.wide-card {
    grid-column: span 2;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-card img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transform: scale(1.01);
    transition: transform 0.6s ease, filter 0.6s ease;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-card::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.82), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)),
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.22), transparent 42%);
    opacity: 0.88;
    transition: opacity 0.35s ease;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-card:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.07);
    filter: contrast(1.06) saturate(1.08);
  }

  .postjoy-factory-card:hover::after {
    opacity: 0.96;
  }

  .postjoy-card-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 26px;
  }

  .postjoy-card-overlay span {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    color: #111111;
    background: #ff7a18;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 1.1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .postjoy-card-overlay h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.18;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .postjoy-card-overlay p {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 520px;
    color: #e7e7e7;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-quality {
    padding: 1px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 122, 24, 0.7), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), rgba(255, 122, 24, 0.25));
  }

  .postjoy-factory-quality-inner {
    padding: 54px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.16), transparent 35%),
      #111111;
    border-radius: 27px;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-quality-inner h3 {
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 38px;
    line-height: 1.18;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-quality-inner > p {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 18px;
    color: #d6d6d6;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.78;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-confidence {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    margin: 38px auto 34px;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-confidence div {
    padding: 24px 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.085);
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-confidence span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: #ff7a18;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-confidence p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .postjoy-factory-bold-line {
    margin-top: 28px !important;
    color: #ffffff !important;
    font-size: 22px !important;
    line-height: 1.55 !important;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .postjoy-factory-story {
      padding: 76px 18px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-header h2 {
      font-size: 46px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-showcase {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      grid-auto-rows: 310px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-card.large-card {
      grid-row: span 1;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-card.wide-card {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-confidence {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 680px) {
    .postjoy-factory-story {
      padding: 58px 16px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-header {
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-eyebrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 1.8px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-header h2 {
      font-size: 34px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-header p,
    .postjoy-factory-intro p,
    .postjoy-factory-quality-inner > p {
      font-size: 15.5px;
      line-height: 1.68;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 42px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-stat {
      padding: 20px 18px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-stat span {
      font-size: 30px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-showcase {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-auto-rows: 360px;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 54px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-card,
    .postjoy-factory-card.large-card,
    .postjoy-factory-card.wide-card {
      grid-column: auto;
      grid-row: auto;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-card {
      min-height: 360px;
      border-radius: 18px;
    }

    .postjoy-card-overlay {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .postjoy-card-overlay h3 {
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .postjoy-card-overlay p {
      font-size: 14.5px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-quality {
      border-radius: 22px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-quality-inner {
      padding: 38px 20px;
      border-radius: 21px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-quality-inner h3 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-confidence {
      gap: 14px;
      margin: 30px auto 28px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-confidence div {
      padding: 20px 18px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-confidence p {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .postjoy-factory-bold-line {
      font-size: 18px !important;
    }
  }
</style>